replies.body:
Hi Odreiw! You can submit a support ticket without logging in by selecting "I need help recovering my account" (submit link: https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new)

If it's a bug we'll help you sort it out :D Another thing worth noting is that your summoner name and your username are different, so when you go to log in to the support site make sure you're using your username if you're not already (if you forget what it is, it's probably saved in the client when you launch it)

Sorry for the trouble, hope we can get it sorted out soon {{summoner:6}}
